Coding Rules:

All Telegram API calls through TgClient using aiohttp

Poller contains NO business logic, only receiving and queueing

Workers execute business logic, work with database

Queue is asyncio.Queue (shared between poller and workers)

Worker count controlled by concurrent_workers parameter

Error handling and logging required

Timers stored in GameState.timer_ends_at and checked by workers